title: Valhalla 14 - The Wall
description:
We are getting closer to the ending of the Valhalla saga, with issue 14, just one to go now :)
Translated by yours truly, and retexted by Chevalley.
This time, its the story of Tjalfe's rite of manhood, love, and how Loki became the mother of Odin's horse, Sleipnir.


So here you go, Valhalla 14 - The Wall

The name is Vassal... Skirnir Vassal. That is the secret identity Tjalfe is assigned when he is sent to Jotunheim. His mission: To persuade the jotunn Gymirâ€™s daughter, Gerd, to go on a date with the god Freyr. It should have been an easy task, but right now, there are rumours about Ragnarok approaching. And a huge army of jotunns is assembling in Gymisgard! 
But does the giant's daughter want to meet with a god, one of their enemies? And how did Loki become the mother of Odin's horse?
This is a story about impossible love!
